- Kim: (1) survival-cell 3/6 -> 6/6 component, (2) nauion-v10 draft
  khong hardcode CELLS array fetch /api/cells, (3) migrate
  packages/event-contracts ts -> nauion paradigm.

Nguyen tac canh:
